setBus

boolean setBus(java.lang.String busId,
               TBus bus)
replace the bus object in the network container. If there is any branch connected to the bus, the branch will be connected to the new object. Also, the bus lookup table will be also updated

Parameters:
busId - bus id
bus - the bus object to be removed

removeBus
